  2002-10-21, Niels: 
   In NS_CACHE.sml, function cacheForAwhile:

   We may consider a more advanced version with a function type of
   (string,'a) -> string, that is 

     val cacheForAwhile : (string*'a -> string) * (string*'a) * int -> (string * 'a) -> string

   This would have been useful in ScsDist

